    "redesign_intro": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "disabled": true,
      "name": "Redesign intro",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"page-width page-width--narrow custom-liquid-redesign\" style=\"padding:1rem 0 2rem; text-align:left;\"><p style=\"font-size:1.6rem; line-height:1.7;\">Some rings stop being worn — an engagement ring from a past chapter, an inherited band that doesn't fit, a style that no longer feels like you. Turning a ring into a necklace keeps everything that matters about it while making it something you'll actually wear.</p><h2>Can you turn my ring into a necklace?</h2><p>Yes. Converting a ring into a pendant or necklace is one of my most popular redesigns. I take your stone and gold and reset them into a new pendant designed around you — the sentiment stays, the form changes.</p><h2>What kinds of rings can become necklaces?</h2><p>Almost any — engagement rings, wedding bands, inherited and heirloom rings, cocktail rings, and rings with sentimental stones. If it holds meaning, it can be reimagined.</p><h2>Can you turn my engagement ring or wedding ring into a pendant?</h2><p>Absolutely. Turning an engagement or wedding ring into a necklace is a meaningful way to keep a piece close after a loss, a divorce, or simply when it no longer suits daily wear. <a href=\"/pages/redesign-engagement-ring\">See engagement ring redesign →</a></p><h2>Will you use my own diamond and gold?</h2><p>Yes. I reset your own diamond and gemstones and responsibly refine your gold toward the new pendant — preserving sentiment, lowering cost, and being kinder to the environment. <a href=\"/pages/use-your-own-gems-metal\">How using your own gold works →</a></p><h2>How much does it cost to turn a ring into a necklace?</h2><p>It depends on the new setting and chain, but because your stone and gold are already yours, it's usually far more affordable than buying new. <a href=\"/pages/jewelry-redesign-cost\">See the pricing guide →</a></p><h2>How do I start?</h2><p>Book a free virtual consultation and send me photos of your ring. I'll design a pendant and give you a transparent quote before any work begins. Everything can be done remotely with insured, tracked shipping.</p><p style=\"margin-top:2.5rem;\"><a href=\"/pages/contact\" class=\"button\">Book your free consultation</a></p></div>",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 24,
        "padding_bottom": 12
      }
    },
